HEADWORD: non-discrimination
<hw>non-discrimination</hw></mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <def>Fairness in treating people without prejudice; --
used mostly in reference to discrimination based on race, religion, and
nationality.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>non-discriminatory</ent>⟦br⟧
